        <briefdescription>
<para>Macro for accessing the NFC NDEF message descriptor instance that you created with <ref refid="group__nfc__ndef__msg_ga912e0302af4c49c3432535b3a44b0166_1ga912e0302af4c49c3432535b3a44b0166" kindref="member">NFC_NDEF_MSG_DEF</ref>. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
        </detaileddescription>
